\"&lt;coding&gt;&lt;system value=&quot;http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-core/CodeSystem/ConsentProvisionCodesCS&quot;&gt;&lt;version value=&quot;7.0.0-ballot&quot;&gt;&lt;code value=&quot;GC&quot;&gt;&lt;display value=&quot;General Consent&quot;&gt;&lt;/coding&gt;\" title=\"Click to Copy as Coding\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"x-http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-core/CodeSystem/ConsentProvisionCodesCS-PATPORTAL\"> </a><code>http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-core/CodeSystem/ConsentProvisionCodesCS</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"CodeSystem-ConsentProvisionCodesCS.html#ConsentProvisionCodesCS-PATPORTAL\">PATPORTAL</a></td><td>Patient Portal</td><td><div><p>Consent given by a patient or legal representative to participate in the patient portal. The patient consents to sharing of their protected health information\nbetween the patient portal and the healthcare facility as specified in the agreement.</p>\n</div></td><td><span class=\"copy-text-inline\"><button data-clipboard-text=\"{&quot;system&quot;: &quot;http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-core/CodeSystem/ConsentProvisionCodesCS&quot;, &quot;version&quot;: &quot;7.0.0-ballot&quot;, &quot;code&quot;: &quot;PATPORTAL&quot;, &quot;display&quot;: &quot;Patient Portal&quot;}\" title=\"Click to Copy as Coding\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></td><td><span class=\"copy-text-inline\"><button data-clipboard-text=\"&lt;coding&gt;&lt;system value=&quot;http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-core/CodeSystem/ConsentProvisionCodesCS&quot;&gt;&lt;version value=&quot;7.0.0-ballot&quot;&gt;&lt;code value=&quot;PATPORTAL&quot;&gt;&lt;display value=&quot;Patient Portal&quot;&gt;&lt;/coding&gt;\" title=\"Click to Copy as Coding\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></td></tr></table></div>"
